<% content_for :page_title, "About" %>

<div class="text-left">
  <h3>About</h3>

  <p><%= site_name %> is a tool for the science fiction computer game
  <a href="https://www.eveonline.com/signup/?invc=7a106e65-1709-4747-9e27-109a4d2774d6"
     rel="noopener nofollow"
     target="_blank">EVE Online</a>.</p>

  <p>It provides a convenient out-of-game access to in-game calendar. Please check
  the complete list of <%= link_to("features", root_path) %>.</p>

  <section class="py-4" id="privacy">
    <h4>Privacy statement</h4>

    <p>The site uses Eve Online's own <%= link_to_eve_online_sso_help("single-sign-on") %> system. No login data is stored.</p>

    <p>The following permissions are requested</p>

    <dl class="px-4">
      <dt class="text-monospace">esi-calendar.read_calendar_events.v1</dt>
      <dd>Allows reading a character's calendar, including corporation events</dd>
    </dl>

    <p>Once granted, permissions can be revoked anytime using the <a href="https://community.eveonline.com/support/third-party-applications/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Third Party Applications</a> management page.</p>

    <div class="alert alert-secondary" role="alert">
      <strong>Note:</strong> <%= site_name %> is open-source. Please feel free to look at or audit <a href="https://github.com/lunohodov/eventical" target="_blank" rel="noopener">the code</a>.
    </div>
  </section>

