    <h5>Build with</h5>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/rails/rails" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ruby on Rails</a> — The back end is a Rails app</li>
      <li><a href="http://www.postgresql.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PostgreSQL</a> — Main data store is in Postgres</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/lunohodov/eventical/blob/master/Gemfile" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Various Ruby libraries</a></li>
    </ul>
    <h5>Icons</h5>
